Problem Approach:

I have used pseudo codes in designing the system.
For the phaseIII implementation I used JAVA program language and wrote seperate modules for all the classes.

No Utilities used.

Bulk Complexities of System:
---------------------------

Number of Code lines	: 3546
Number of comment lines : 251
Number of Declarations  : 224
Executable Statements   : 114
Blank Lines             : 212
Number of Decisions     : 182
Number of Methods       : 85
Number of Classes	: 21


