Time Spent on Designing : 30 hours
Time Spent on Coding    : 25 hours
Time Spend on Testing   : 25 hours (includes debugging)

		
As Java being platform independent my simulation is most likely portable to other operating systems.

As Java being an object oriented language so that to modularize the code, I used Java programming language.
